high_descs: Turn around and go to the dresser.
Pick up the soap dispenser on the dresser.
Turn around and go to the toilet.
Put the soap dispenser on the toilet.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Pick up the soap dispenser on the sink.
Turn around and go to the toilet.
Put the soap dispenser on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Move two soap dispensers to the toilet.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the white counter on the right side.
Pick up the bottle of lotion behind the yellow spray bottle.
Turn around and face the toilet on the left.
Place the bottle of lotion on the back of the toilet to the left of the candle.
Walk to the front of the sink on the right.
Pick up the bottle of lotion that's to the right of the sink faucet.
Turn and walk back to the toilet.
Place the second bottle of lotion on the back of the toilet to the right of the candle.
anns.task_desc: Move two bottles of lotion to the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn around and walk until you turn to your right and face a chest of drawers
Pick up a perfume bottle from the chest of drawers
Turn around so you are on the left side of the toilet, facing the toilet paper holder
Set the perfume bottle down on the back of the toilet
Walk to your right and then turn left to face the sink
Pick up a perfume bottle from the sink
Go back to where you were just standing at the toilet
Set this perfume bottle down on the back of the toilet on the far side
anns.task_desc: Put two perfume bottles on the toilet
